Package org.apache.jena.sparql.util

Class Iso

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.sparql.util.Iso
  • public class Iso
extends java.lang.Object
    Isomorphism utilities, based in order lists. See IsoMatcher for isomorphism for un-ordered collections. In this class, "isomorphism" is based on the policy in NodeIsomorphismMap, which is blank node isomorphism unless NodeIsomorphismMap.makeIsomorphic(org.apache.jena.graph.Node, org.apache.jena.graph.Node) is overridden.
